OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,FA new scheme to tackle the chronic
OL,7,Flack of rural doctors in Dumfries and
OL,8,FGalloway has taken a step forward.
OL,10,FTrainee doctors can now use state of
OL,11,Fthe art teaching facilities at the
OL,12,FUniversity of West of Scotland (UWS)
OL,13,Fin Dumfries.
OL,15,FHealth bosses and university heads
OL,16,Fhave signed an agreement which means
OL,17,Fup to 20 students can practice their
OL,18,Fskills in a realistic setting with
OL,19,Fmannequins standing in as real
OL,20,Fpatients.
