OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,FThe Universities of Dundee and St
OL,7,FAndrews have joined with the
OL,8,FUniversity of West of Scotland and the
OL,9,FGovernment's ScotGEM scheme - a four-
OL,10,Fyear graduate-entry medical programme.
OL,12,FThe new facilities have been designed
OL,13,Fto be identical to wards and
OL,14,Fdepartments at D&G Hospital, but also
OL,15,Fhave 'home' settings and GP surgeries
OL,16,Fso students can learn as close to real-
OL,17,Flife as possible.
