OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,FThe course is designed to develop
OL,7,Fdoctors interested in a career as a
OL,8,Fgeneralist practitioner within NHS
OL,9,FScotland, with an emphasis on rural
OL,10,Fneeds
OL,12,FHistorically, Dumfries and Galloway
OL,13,Fhas had one of the lowest numbers of
OL,14,FGPs in Scotland.
OL,16,FThe latest headcount survey shows that
OL,17,Fthe region had 69 GPs per 100,000
OL,18,Fpopulation - less than the national
OL,19,Faverage for Scotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
