OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,FAnd more than 40% of surgeries
OL,7,Freported vacancies - the highest
OL,8,Ffigure in mainland Scotland.
OL,10,FSo far 17 people are in the first
OL,11,F'Crichton Cohort' - so called because
OL,12,Fof the campus where they will be
OL,13,Fstudying.
OL,15,FIt's hoped the new group will be one
OL,16,Fof many which could help reverse the
OL,17,Fdecline in rural doctors.
OL,19,FMusa Zahir, originally from Woking, is
OL,20,Fin his second year as a ScotGem
OL,21,Fmedical student.
