OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,FHe said he was inspired to become a
OL,7,Frural doctor because of his previous
OL,8,Fstudies in medical sciences at Swansea
OL,9,FUniversity.
OL,11,F"While studying there, I realised the
OL,12,Fsocial inequalities and the
OL,13,Fdifferences in healthcare received by
OL,14,Fpeople who live in urban areas and
OL,15,Fthose who live in remote and rural
OL,16,Fareas, especially those who have
OL,17,Fdifficulties accessing hospitals.
OL,19,F"And part of what drove me into
OL,20,Fmedicine is that I want to combat
OL,21,Fthose inequalities."
