OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,FHeather Knaggs has been a pharmacist
OL,7,Fin Dumfries for 20 years but is now
OL,8,Fgetting the chance to complete a
OL,9,Fmedical degree.
OL,11,F"It's a great privilege to be able to
OL,12,Fstudy medicine in this region.
OL,14,F"Medicine was always an ambition which
OL,15,FI thought had passed me by. But
OL,16,FScotGEM opened the opportunity for me
OL,17,Fto proceed. So I grabbed it.
