OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,F"We know that we have a shortage of
OL,7,FGP's within Dumfries and Galloway and
OL,8,FScotGEM is one of the multiple ways
OL,9,Fwe're trying to address that
OL,10,Fdifficulty and trying to encourage
OL,11,Fpeople to come and work and experience
OL,12,Four local area in the hope they will
OL,13,Fcome back as GPs but also hospital
OL,14,Fdoctors and work in the local area as
OL,15,Fwell."
OL,17,FJames Miller, UWS principal and vice-
OL,18,Fchancellor said the new cooperation
OL,19,Fwith ScotGEM would help "fully recruit
OL,20,Fand retain doctors for the future".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
