OL,3,CHomegrown doctors could help the
OL,4,Cchronic shortage of rural GPs
OL,6,F"The ScotGEM scheme has been working
OL,7,Ffor some years now. So the first
OL,8,Fcohort has already graduated. And this
OL,9,Fis about continuing that graduation
OL,10,Fcohorts throughout the coming years."
OL,12,FEven when the students have completed
OL,13,Fthis course it can take a further five
OL,14,Fbefore they are fully qualified, so
OL,15,Fthis scheme is likely to be a longer
OL,16,Fterm solution to the problem of GP
OL,17,Fvacancies in South West Scotland.
